            <title><![CDATA[【🙉#使用耳机606060原则保护耳朵#】如何正确使用耳机，记住“60-60-60”原则：①环境声音不超过60分贝；②戴耳机音量不超过功率的60%；③连续戴耳机时间不超...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【🙉<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80%B3%E6%9C%BA606060%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E8%80%B3%E6%9C%B5%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80%B3%E6%9C%BA606060%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E8%80%B3%E6%9C%B5%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#使用耳机606060原则保护耳朵#</span></a>】如何正确使用耳机，记住“60-60-60”原则：①环境声音不超过60分贝；②戴耳机音量不超过功率的60%；③连续戴耳机时间不超过60分钟。此外，尽量避免在嘈杂的环境中停留过久，避免使用尖锐物品掏耳朵，擤鼻涕时不要同时捏住两侧鼻翼用力👇🏻<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4875324786409517" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hbn0flple8j61og0y0hb302.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/ibdbXIAKlx083AqzwjqM010412006KoC0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1678070216&amp;ssig=tN0AhECLhx&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/yH1AOnpFlx083AqzLmEw010412003sM40E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1678070216&amp;ssig=80iCzangly&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/kvJU8Cislx083AqzrUEg010412002eW50E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1678070216&amp;ssig=1P9IzkCJXK&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4875324786409517&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
